@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Welcome to the Digital Product World";
}

<style>
    /* General Body Styling */
    body {
        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f2f9fc; /* Pastel blue background */
        color: #333;
    }

    /* Hero Section Styling */
    .hero-section {
        color: #fff;
        padding: 120px 20px;
        text-align: center;
        border-bottom: 4px solid #ffffff;
        background-color: #003366; /* Darker background for the final welcome section */
    }

        .hero-section h1 {
            font-size: 3.5em;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .hero-section p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .hero-section .btn-get-started {
            padding: 12px 25px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: #6b9bff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-top: 20px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

            .hero-section .btn-get-started:hover {
                background-color: #6b9bff;
                color: #fff;
            }

    /* Description Section */
    .description-section {
        text-align: left;
        padding: 60px 20px;
        font-size: 0.95em; /* Smaller text size */
        color: #333;
    }

        .description-section p {
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .description-section .highlight {
            color: #003366; /* Dark Blue */
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.2em; /* Adjusted font size */
        }

        .description-section h3 {
            font-size: 1.8em; /* Smaller h3 size */
            color: #003366; /* Dark Blue */
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

    /* Key Features Section */
    .features-section {
        padding: 60px 20px;
        text-align: center;
    }

        .features-section h2 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            color: #6b9bff;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .features-section .feature {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 30%;
            margin: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: left;
        }

            .features-section .feature h3 {
                font-size: 1.6em;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
                color: #333;
            }

            .features-section .feature p {
                font-size: 1.1em;
                color: #666;
            }

    /* Footer Styling */
    footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px 0;
        background-color: #003366 ;
    }

        footer p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }

</style>

<div class="description-section">
    <p class="highlight"><h3><b>Welcome to the Digital Product World</b>!</h3> we provide a comprehensive platform for managing and showcasing digital products. whether you're a business looking to expand your digital presence or a customer searching for the latest digital tools, our site offers everything you need to manage and present digital products seamlessly.</p>

    <p>our platform focuses on simplicity and user experience, ensuring that both sellers and buyers can navigate with ease. from adding new products to managing inventories, we provide an intuitive, secure, and highly scalable environment to grow your digital business.</p>

    <h3>Easy Product Management</h3>
    <p>we allow businesses to easily add and manage their products. the intuitive interface makes it simple for you to keep your digital product catalog up to date, no matter how many products you offer.</p>

    <h3>Customizable Product Showcase</h3>
    <p>our platform is designed to help you showcase your digital products in the best light. customize your product listings with detailed descriptions, media files, and more to make a lasting impression on your customers.</p>

    <h3>Advanced Security Features</h3>
    <p>your data and transactions are important to us. our platform incorporates the latest in security measures to ensure that your information remains private and safe at all times. with our secure payment gateway and user data protection protocols, you can trust that your business is in good hands.</p>

    <h3>Seamless Transactions</h3>
    <p>our secure and efficient payment processing system ensures that all transactions are quick and hassle-free. buyers can enjoy a smooth checkout experience while sellers can track orders easily in real-time.</p>

    <h3>Responsive Design</h3>
    <p>the platform is fully responsive, making it easy to access and manage products from any device, be it desktop, tablet, or smartphone. your customers can browse and purchase digital products from anywhere, at any time.</p>

    <h3>Continuous Updates and Support</h3>
    <p>we are committed to continually improving the platform. our dedicated support team is always here to assist you, and we roll out regular updates to enhance functionality and user experience.</p>

    <h3>Analytics and Insights</h3>
    <p>our platform provides powerful analytics to help you track sales, customer behavior, and more. with detailed reports and insights, you can make data-driven decisions that fuel business growth.</p>

    <h3>Why Choose Us?</h3>
    <p>we aim to provide the best platform for businesses to manage and showcase their digital products. our secure, user-friendly interface combined with advanced features makes us a top choice for digital product management.</p>
</div>

<div class="features-section">
    <h2>Key Features of Our Website</h2>
    <div class="feature">
        <h3>Easy Product Management</h3>
        <p>our website allows users to easily manage and add new products, making it convenient for businesses to showcase their offerings with minimal effort.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
        <h3>Responsive Design</h3>
        <p>with a fully responsive design, you can explore our products seamlessly on any device, whether it's a desktop, tablet, or mobile phone.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
        <h3>Secure Payments</h3>
        <p>we ensure secure and hassle-free payment methods, ensuring peace of mind for both sellers and buyers.</p>
    </div>
</div>

